    "key_insight": "1227 vs 33 training samples is the headline improvement. The model learns shared central banking logic: inflation\u2192hike, deflation/crisis\u2192cut, uncertainty\u2192hold. Individual leader behavior is encoded via fixed profile embeddings (16D from behavioral parameters). Leaders with distinctive profiles (Bernanke, Zhou, Greenspan) show higher LOLO accuracy \u2014 the profile embedding provides informative conditioning even when the test leader's data was unseen."
